data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":227,"item_id":"msg_26ec235af7438fbf0069351afcc8d48190a7e309544f44ce75","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso Galaxy Innovations offers a range of smart eyewear products called SmartView Glasses. These glasses come equipped with several advanced features:\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: This feature provides an enhanced viewing experience by overlaying digital information onto the real world.\n\n2. **Voice-controlled AI Agent**: The glasses are equipped with an AI that you can control using voice commands, allowing for hands-free operation.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Capture high-definition videos accompanied by immersive 3D audio quality, perfect for recording experiences or events.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Protect your eyes with built-in UV protection while minimizing eye strain through blue light filtering.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: Enjoy the convenience of wireless charging, coupled with a long-lasting battery, ensuring your glasses are ready to use throughout the day.\n\nAdditional details include a user guide that covers various aspects such as introduction, product overview, sizing, care and maintenance, safety tips, and troubleshooting, along with warranty information and contact support.","logprobs":[]}

